metadata.name: Yin Yang
metadata.description:
She was a radiant sun, bursting with joy,  
her light shining bright, a beacon to all.  
He was a moon, his light dim and coy,  
seeking her glow.  
She saw his darkness, and reached out her hand,  
Offering her light, to bring him back to life,  
He felt her warmth, and began to understand,  
That maybe his world could be more than strife.
